<p><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 3px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">春光明媚，草长莺飞。</strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 3px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">在全国第45个植树节之际，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 3px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">为深入学习宣传贯彻党的二十大精神，全面践行习近平生态文明思想，传承弘扬雷锋精神，树立和践行绿水青山就是金山银山的理念，唤起经济管理学院学子植树造林、绿化环境、美化校园生活的环保意识。</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 3px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">2023年3月12日下午，经济管理学院学生党员、27期、28期入党积极分子、劳动协会在刘孟老师的带领下一起参加植树节活动。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/2n18Qa8gmEJRU3hWbEFxhPud0sPTGOESGs1LLoe9BNQ6ostPNhNRDWj0SwOBy8Uh3m4OHt4BeEQY9tHWuhJkCw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1" alt="图片" width="256" height="168" style="width: 256px; height: 168px;"/></p><p><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 3px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">分工明确，相互配合。</strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 3px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">在活动开始前，每位同学都分配好劳动工具，拔草、挖坑、播种、覆土，一气呵成。每一个步骤都做得一丝不苟，经历了一番植树的辛劳，大家虽然汗流浃背、气喘吁吁，但是看着埋下的种子，脸上无不洋溢着欢乐的笑容，洋溢着鲜亮而青春的色彩。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 3px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/2n18Qa8gmEJRU3hWbEFxhPud0sPTGOESRJX1GMB7x7ycGSMc9MicVzprVyyOeNfWko67mgM7icBwy3mtkF6lS8MQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1" alt="图片" width="236" height="164" style="width: 236px; height: 164px;"/></span></p>